Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 78<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/24/01 7:43:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> Hail<br><br>Lightstones and Greater Lightstones are magic.  They are affected by TLC.  Burned out Lightstones are either Lore or Magic (I'm all but certain) and are also affected by TLC.  Yes, some things for research are caught by TLC, just as some things for quests, trade skills, and many other needs are caught by TLC.  Just part of the fun.<br><br>Valquiss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ugrimwyrd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimwyrd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 64<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/24/01 1:50:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> Aye, they are affected by TLC. You'll just need to buy any lightstones you need from youngsters. The key is to watch for a message which says that &quot;the creature was trivial for you or your group&quot; when you kill it. <p>Grimwyrd Storm<BR>(Lux Aeternam)<BR>28th Human Druid of Karana<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ugolsec.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Golsec</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/24/01 8:49:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.cloudk.clara.net/storage/golavatar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> Yup, TLC'd.<br>Nice that the greedy types can't kill them in front of the low level who was trying to hunt them, but it's a real pain for magicians at least <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Ah well, just part of this server's charm <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>(Honest! The good points do outweigh the bad) <p>-- <br><img src="http://www.cloudk.clara.net/storage/golsecsig.jpg"><br>(Also known as Cloudien, Druid of The Rathe server)<br>Insert lame joke here</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/upakuachuan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PakuaChuan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/26/01 12:12:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> Golsec,<br><br>Pain for monks as well. the other day spent an hour pulling wisps to nearby groups and then fd'ing so that they could kill the mob when it was halfdead, but they kept telling me no gls's dropped. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   (not sure if I was being duped or not--oh well)  Monks need one for sash quest. <p>Pakua Chuan <BR>Humble monk and disciple of Quellious<BR>Member of Starspun<BR> <BR>"You can discover more about a person in an hour of play than in a year of conversation." -- Plato</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ufalconeroftunare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Falconer of Tunare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 38<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/26/01 10:04:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> I have some GLS's for you Pakua <p><center><img src="http://members.aol.com/jimturner99/gyrhawk"></center> <b><center>Gyrhawk - Tunare's Falconer</center></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utukka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tukka</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/26/01 5:55:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.atlantic.net/~tukka/hand.gif height=42 width=42></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> GLSes ought to be TLC'd, but I know for a fact that I picked up both lighstones and greater lightstones off green-conning wisps in Befallen about a week ago.  I was surprised, but I even double-checked after I got the first lightstone.  I conned the next wisp I saw (it was green), I killed it (got no experience message, nor did I get a trivial message) and got a GLS off it.<br><br>I was level 20 at the time, and there was a level 21 character in our group.<br><br>Also note: You would be getting a &quot;this kill was trivial for your group&quot; message if you were being affected by TLC.  If you aren't getting this message, then you're just the victim of bad luck and not TLC.  I killed upwards of 35 wisps when they were still conning even/blue to me before I got my first lighstone or greater lightstone, so such strains of bad luck are not unheardof. <p><FONT FACE="Comic Sans MS">--Tukka</FONT><BR>EverQuest characters:<BR>Tukka (Brell Serilis)<BR>Velsor (Firiona Vie)<BR>Xumbraxa (Torvonnilous)<BR>Tuono (Morell-Thule)<BR>Quinsta (The Seventh Hammer)<BR>Crink (Rallos Zek)</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utukka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tukka</A> at: 12/26/01 5:58:30 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/upakuachuan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PakuaChuan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/26/01 10:24:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> I have gottent the trivial message for willowisps. Not sure why you did not get this message. Might have to go hunt in Befallen if that be the case. <p>Pakua Chuan <BR>Humble monk and disciple of Quellious<BR>Member of Starspun<BR> <BR>"You can discover more about a person in an hour of play than in a year of conversation." -- Plato</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uxenojones.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XENOJONES</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/27/01 2:13:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> There are higher level wisps in Stonebrunt mountains if you need to get a GLS. I think they are called a nature spirit or something like that. They are around 22nd level. Also there are some wisps in Unrest.<br><br>Eventually wisps will be trivial to almost everybody on the server........<br><br>An example where TLC is bad <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br>Rollen<br>Champion of Resolution <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uvelondradreamweaver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Velondra Dreamweaver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/27/01 4:08:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=954.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GLSs TLCd?</span><hr size=1> As far as the Concordance of Research goes, look around at some of the caster vendors; I saw one for 11pp or so in the Mage guild in Erudin. Also, check the vendors in zones where wisps live (like WC)--I've seen LS and GLS for sale there.<br><br><br>Velondra Dreamweaver,<br>Voleuse de Reves <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrev